What and Why
&ldquo;Amma coffee thaaa !&rdquo;
has been one constant in my life for the past 15-16 years now. It has transformed from a mere sentence to an emotion. Over time, I evolved into an avid coffee drinker, consuming more than the average amount. I began exploring coffee at various places, delving into the nuances of different types. In this blog, I will document and share my experiences with the diverse world of coffee.
